titles.title: Commending the Southeastern Wildlife Exposition for its 40 years of celebrating the great outdoors.
Commending the Southeastern Wildlife Exposition for its 40 years of celebrating the great outdoors.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Natural Resources.

bill.summary: This resolution congratulates the Southeastern Wildlife Exposition, a nonprofit organization in Charleston, South Carolina, on its 40th anniversary for its festivals promoting wildlife conservation, education, and the arts.
